{"tid":715964,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【死獌狗】保羅普巴揚言今屆是他最後一屆世界盃","createTime":"2018-06-25T01:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T02:09:03.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a589c597a204169f91505577dedcc9702b2741a7","tid":715964,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T01:32:48.000Z","msg":"法國中場保羅普巴，自從2016年轉投曼聯後，表現長期受到批評，就算回到國家隊亦一樣。「高盧雄雞」C組已穩入16強，普巴在尾輪對丹麥前表示，希望將批評聲音拋諸腦後，更透露這是他最後一屆世盃。<br />\n <br />\n普巴（中）過去兩仗表現未算突出。（路透社）<br />\n法國在C組已穩奪出線權，尾輪對丹麥只要和波就可以首名出線。25歲的普巴對澳洲、秘魯均有上陣，分組賽最終戰前接受訪問，希望可以為法國在20年後再奪世盃。普巴說：「為了法國，我會全力以赴，我真的想贏得世界盃。」"},{"pid":"8e2cf8bb257442fbdf592615e5f0361008509c90","tid":715964,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T01:34:29.000Z","msg":"下届29歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39675b28d027fab6c7ea420c9a4af5e71bc6f733","tid":715964,"uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8e2cf8bb257442fbdf592615e5f0361008509c90","tid":715964,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T01:34:29.000Z","msg":"下届29歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T01:37:10.000Z","msg":"4年內逝世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a6b8f0d4e6eb2053ef5688c9085b2cdb5d2321","tid":715964,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T01:37:50.000Z","msg":"法國大把人用"},{"pid":"3e398833625324b6698293e2c4edb286137b6742","tid":715964,"uid":15862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T01:43:02.000Z","msg":"邊到有講係最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066f61d0e2a29e45f2325436099b0678748a81fc","tid":715964,"uid":174013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T02:09:03.000Z","msg":"弱智樓主又自己改標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}